    "First, we argue on understanding biases, not bias, as a multifaceted issue.",
    "Then, we criticize the AI assumption of ground truth, quest for source criticism and archival practices, and discuss the issue of reliable data annotation.",
    "Finally, we claim for approaches specific to data types and domain types.",
    "A summary of the challenges, policy advices, and best practices in understanding bias is reported in Fig. 3.",
